Variables List

Simulation Object

sim.num_states # number of quantum states 
sim.temp # temperature 

sim.mass # classical oscillator mass 
sim.pq_weight # classical oscillator auxiliary parameter # formerly sim.h
sim.h_c_params # parameters for classical Hamiltonian 
h_c_vars # variables for classical Hamiltonian 
sim.h_qc_params # parameters for quantum-classical Hamiltonian 
sim.h_q_params # parameters for quantum Hamiltonian 
sim.h_c # classical Hamiltonian
sim.h_qc # quantum-classical Hamiltonian
sim.h_q # quantum Hamiltonain
sim.dh_qc_dzc # dH_qc/dz*
sim.dh_qc_dz # dH_qc/dz -- should be made optional
sim.dh_c_dzc # dH_c/dz*

